\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\f7\lang2057\f9\fs24\f7\lang1025\qj\tx540 6.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\qj\tx540{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af7\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f7\fs24\lang2057\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 According to the Commission the abuse that is alleged in this case commenced in about April 1999 and by the end of the hearing (December 2004) was believed to still be continuing. Nevertheless the evidence we have had presented in this case has not always 
correlated with that period or with any consistent time period. The Commission has provided some figures for the period ending March 2001 (travel agents sales figures and sales of airline tickets at Johannesburg International), others for the period ending
 May 2001(Table B in figures bundle 2 a comparison of travel agency flown revenue and BSP), some for June 2001 (Table E2 which relates to passenger information on BA/Comair), and yet others until October 2004 (Table G figures bundle 2 which relates to pass
enger sales on Nationwide). }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj\tx540{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li540\ri0\lin540\rin0\fi-540\rtlch\af7\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f7\fs24\lang2057\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\f7\lang2057\f9\fs24\f7\lang1025\qj\tx540 7.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\qj\tx540{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af7\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f7\fs24\lang2057\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 Perhaps the reason for this unevenness in selection is that information was collected at different times during the long life of this case and earlier information was not updated to conform to a common endpoint.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s15{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs45\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 The Commission is not solely culpable on this count. SAA has also sought information, from BA/Comair for instance, over a wide period. See summons to BA/Comair for periods 1997 to the present. See transcript 19 August 2004 at page 321.}}}
{\*\cs45\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af14\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af14\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177 } We do not wish to exaggerate the difficulti
es in these inconsistencies as some of the information is of less probative value than others or the use of different periods has been appropriate because the data is being employed to illustrate different points. }
