when its investigative period ended.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s15{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs45\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 See affidavit of Menzi Simelane on remedies paragraph 11.}}}
{\*\cs45\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af14\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af14\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177 } We will refer to this from now on in the decision as the \'91relevant period\'92. This is a period for which most of the more important information on effects is presented, although we will, for the purpose of interpreting i
