 appear to be the subject of negotiation between the firm and SAA. In the agreement with American Express, the agency is required to achieve an annual growth of 25% from its target in the preceding financial year.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057\i\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s15{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs45\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 See clause 5.4, Record page 438 }}}
