\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s18\qj\tx720{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af7\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f7\fs24\lang2057\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\f7\lang2057\i\f9\fs24\i\f7\lang1025\i\qj\tx540 19.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s18\qj\tx540{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af7\afs24\lang1025\ai\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f7\fs24\lang2057\i\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057\i{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs24\lang2057\i\b0{ It is not clear from the evidence as to whether SAA introduced the override scheme into the market or whether they reacted to what British Airlines was doing internationally. Nothing turns on this. What we do know is that when SAA first introduced the sche
