r this reason we give SAA the benefit of finding that the abuse in this case is only shown to have lasted a period of approximately 20 months.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s15{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs45\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 During his opening address counsel for the Commission referred to the fact that the \'91reference period\'92 for the agreements, by which we think he meant their duration, varied between one and five years. Nevertheless this information has not been placed befo
re us in evidence.}}}
